<task id="task-1737" class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">Configure BDD Settings</title><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><context class="- topic/section task/context "><p class="- topic/p ">You can configure BDD Settings in Katalon TestOps to upload BDD
         Test Results automatically. Follow these steps:</p></context><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Sign in to <xref format="html" href="https://testops.katalon.io/login" scope="external" class="- topic/xref ">Katalon
                  TestOps</xref> and go to your Project.</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click on the <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Settings</i> icon at the top right corner, and
               choose <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Project Settings</uicontrol>.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image width="400" href="image/to-project-settings.png" class="- topic/image "/></info><stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult "><p class="- topic/p ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Project Settings</uicontrol> page appears.</p></stepresult></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Scroll down to the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Configurations</uicontrol> section, then
               check the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Enable BDD reports</uicontrol> box.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image width="850" href="image/to-enable-bdd.png" class="- topic/image "/></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Save</uicontrol>.</cmd></step></steps></taskbody></task>